    "Workup": {
      "text": "With clear history, no further work up is indicated\nWith altered mental status or ambiguous presentation consider:\nUrinalysis\n, CBC, BMP, LFTs\nCT head\ntox workup\ninfectious work up",
      "subsections": {},
